{"type":null,"faqId":17813,"title":"麦芒C199打开百度地图APK，百度地图里面指南针朝向与实际方向有角度偏差,该如何处理？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">百度地图利用了指南针进行方向识别，如果发现与实际方向有偏差，建议用手机划“8”字校准，消除底噪，否则因为周围磁场电场之类的导致一些方向偏差。“8”字校准的方法为：打开百度地图后，把手机想象成一支笔，手握紧后在空中写2~3个“8”字即可。<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"552","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420012716000,"seriesProductName":"C199-CL00","visitedTimes":163,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"麦芒C199,百度地图,APK,指南针,角度偏差,误差","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}